<lb n="0493c07" ed="T"/>王　<note n="0493011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">琉＝瑠【三】＊</note><note n="0493011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">琉【大】＊，瑠【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0493011"><lem wit="【大】">琉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】 【明】">瑠</rdg></app>璃光龍王　金色髮龍王　金光龍王
<lb n="0493c08" ed="T"/>　月光<note n="0493012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔相〕－【明】</note><note n="0493012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">相【大】，〔－〕【明】</note><app n="0493012"><lem wit="【大】">相</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>龍王　日光龍王　始興龍王　牛
